review:
This game was a lot of fun if this was a serious game, expected more, if this was a ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ good enough. I feel the weapons are more references to the other game then game play changing and the combo system is the only playstyle. The weapon evolution system seems like MUST INCLUDE because of other game and don't quite pack the same punch, minus the birds. Then the Dark-circle-card-counter-system that seems like a band aid rather then balancing. Crawlers have interesting abilities and being able to use 3 at a time is just ♥♥♥♥♥♥♥ too much for my brain. There are enemies in this game that do things but they are few and far between to notice(IE the red banshees). 

Main City is great vibe, voice actors nailed it(music person was all song references), unlock system is overwhelming but that is a good thing when you have a good run and see 9 unlocks, got most of the achievements without hunting them down and again; 

REALLY FUN. I put 20 hours in 3 days, maybe 3 days I don't remember...

Worth it
Got only two complains:
- wildcards are too OP making the game too easy;
- progress happens too fast;

Vampire Survivors - героин; 
Vampire Crawlers - очень героин 3д;
помогите
